Traditional authorities

The following table lists HIV prevalence among 15 to 49-year olds and population across the same age range for all traditional authorities in Mwanza.

Traditional Authority HIV Prevalence Viral load suppression HIV viraemia
Kanduku 4.5% (2.4 to 7.7%) 89.6% (75.1 to 97.1%) 0.5% (0.1 to 1.3%)
Majete Game Reserve - Mwanza NA (NA to NA) NA (NA to NA) NA (NA to NA)
Mwanza Boma 5.0% (2.6 to 9.0%) 89.3% (73.6 to 97.1%) 0.5% (0.1 to 1.5%)
Nthache 4.3% (2.2 to 7.3%) 89.6% (74.9 to 97.1%) 0.4% (0.1 to 1.2%)
STA Govati 3.9% (2.0 to 6.9%) 90.7% (77.5 to 97.5%) 0.4% (0.1 to 1.0%)
